    <item>
      <title>报告称澳大利亚第二大养老金公司增持新西兰 Powerco 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/australia-s-no-2-pension-boosts-stake-in-nz-s-powerco-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《澳大利亚金融评论报》报道，澳大利亚退休信托基金是澳大利亚第二大养老基金，管理着超过 3000 亿澳元（2030 亿美元）的资产，该基金已增持新西兰能源分销商 Powerco Ltd. 的股份，成为其最大股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/australia-s-no-2-pension-boosts-stake-in-nz-s-powerco-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 22:49:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据和美联储讲话后亚洲股市将下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asian-stocks-set-to-drop-after-jobs-data-fedspeak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业数据好坏参半，且美联储态度不明确，加剧了人们对央行降息时间过长的担忧，亚洲股市有望下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/asian-stocks-set-to-drop-after-jobs-data-fedspeak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 22:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
